{"title":"论说话时“一个”的滥用","uid":"d22c4ef61b6f5d170d48760438011003","slug":"论说话时“一个”的滥用","date":"2019-07-21T14:57:35.000Z","updated":"2022-12-30T16:59:45.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/论说话时“一个”的滥用.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<p>不知从什么时候开始，常常听到一些人说话总爱加上几个“<strong>一个</strong>”，让人听着别扭，却又不是什么大毛病，让人说也不是、不说也不是；更重要的是，一旦有人发现了这一点，他/她就会一直专注于这一点而部分忽略讲述人所传达的其他信息，还憋的心里发慌（此处使用微小的夸张手法）。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>……我们要创造<strong>一个</strong>良好的氛围……</p>\n<p>……<strong>一个</strong>这样的<strong>一个</strong>表现手法……</p>\n<p>……这样的<strong>一个</strong>安排会给别人带来<strong>一个</strong>比较差的<strong>一个</strong>感受…..</p>\n<p>……</p></blockquote>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<p>一开始我以为这只是个人习惯，但后来发现，这种现象越来越常见，甚至于每天都会听见有人这样说话，尤其是销售员、推销员一类人。这种别扭的感觉，在我某次坐车听收音机时达到了顶峰。那是一条本地某著名电台播出的广告，主持人先说了一句某某某话剧团要在我们本地大剧院演出什么的，然后就是那个话剧团的团长（应该是吧）开始说话了，大致内容如下：</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>我们这次呢，是要在这<strong>一个</strong> ×× 大剧院里进行我们的<strong>一个</strong>巡回演出，大家可以带上自己的家人啊，朋友啊来一起看我们的<strong>一个</strong>演出。那么在票价这<strong>一个</strong>方面呢，我们是有 ××× 元、××× 元、××× 元还有 ××× 元这样的<strong>一个</strong>价位的<strong>一个</strong>设置……</p></blockquote>\n<p>你看，短短的一段话，出现了 6 个“<strong>一个</strong>”，这很明显是过于冗杂的，看着也不舒服。如果把这段话里的“<strong>一个</strong>”全部去掉，有趣的事情就发生了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ghproxy.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dmnbme/blogfiles/main/images/eCMUhV.jpg\"></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>我们这次呢，是要在这 ×× 大剧院里进行我们的巡回演出，大家可以带上自己的家人啊，朋友啊来一起看我们的演出。那么在票价这方面呢，我们是有 ××× 元、××× 元、××× 元还有 ××× 元这样的价位的设置……</p></blockquote>\n<p>你再看，去除了“<strong>一个</strong>”的这段话是不是更加自然了？而且意思也没变，还节省了字数，更好地体现出汉语的高效性等等好处。</p>\n<p>那么这种现象到底是怎么来的？我也不知道，于是上谷歌搜了一下，发现 × 乎有人回答过<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/294023929\">这个问题</a>，但似乎不是很全面，因此我要去找个高人探讨一波再来接着写。</p>\n<hr>\n<p><em><strong>探讨完之后可能会接着写的地方</strong></em></p>\n<hr>\n<p>PS. 本文中所有的“<strong>一个</strong>”都已加粗（可能看不出来）</p>\n","text":"不知从什么时候开始，常常听到一些人说话总爱加上几个“一个”，让人听着别扭，却又不是什么大毛病，让人说也不是、不说也不是；更重要的是，一旦有人发现了这一点，他/她就会一直专注于这一点而部分忽略讲述人所传达的其他信息，还憋的心里发慌（此处使用微小的夸张手法）。 ……我们要创造一个良好...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":853,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"日常","slug":"日常","count":11,"path":"api/categories/日常.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Beep Beep","slug":"Beep-Beep","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Beep-Beep.json"},{"name":"吐槽","slug":"吐槽","count":1,"path":"api/tags/吐槽.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"Mai","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://dmnb.me/images/avatar.png","link":"/","description":"Idealist / Perfectionist / Freedomist","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"公园溜达（记）","uid":"4b9fceae86484e4c2cce79e8f1071df4","slug":"公园溜达（记）","date":"2019-07-23T13:51:55.000Z","updated":"2020-01-16T05:45:00.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/公园溜达（记）.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"放假了，整个人都舒坦了、放松了、悠闲了，活的像个中老年人一样（误）。 众所周知，中国学生放假，实质上就是换个地儿写作业。在如此多作业的重压之下，即使暑假再怎么舒坦、放松